1b:T40e,Product is clearly a bioabsorbable interference screw system for knee ligament reconstruction. Internal evidence is comprehensive and consistent: PLLA+HA composite material, designed for single-point graft fixation in ACL/PCL procedures. The material composition (PLLA for mechanical stability, HA for osteoconduction) is well-defined. Division (Sports Medicine) and category (Knee Arthroscopy) align perfectly with interference screw application. However, brand field is empty despite clear 'BIO-FERENCE' naming in title/heading/family. No external verification available and no SKU examples to validate size range or specific configurations. Current classification material specs match description. Review required to: 1) Confirm BIO-FERENCE as manufacturer brand vs. product line brand, 2) Validate this represents complete product family vs. single variant, 3) Obtain SKU data to understand product range completeness. Confidence 0.85 based on strong internal consistency but lack of external validation and missing brand attribution.17:["$","$L1a",null,{"product":{"product_name":"BIO-FERENCE PLLA+HA Bio-Absorbable Interference Screw","product_name_display":"BIO-FERENCE PLLA+HA Bio-Absorbable Interference Screw","sku_code":"MA-KIB70025","product_family":"BIO-FERENCE PLLA+HA Bio-Absorbable Interference Screw","product_family_display":"BIO-FERENCE PLLA+HA Bio-Absorbable Interference Screw","slug":"bio-ference-pllaplusha-bio-absorbable-interference-screw","images":[{"storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/spm-brochure/cover_c84c31b4.jpg","filename":"spm_cover_c84c31b4.jpg","source":"brochure_cover"}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"agile-ortho/brochures/sports-medicine-catalog.pdf","seo_meta_title":"BIO-FERENCE PLLA+HA Bio-Absorbable Interference Screw | BIO-FERENCE Knee Arthroscopy - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"Bioabsorbable interference screw made from Poly-L-Lactic Acid (PLLA) and Hydroxyapatite (HA). PLLA ensures long-term mec